                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>Although the pair will always be connected by Duke and the SEC, it is a missing piece of memorabilia that may be the deepest thread between the current and former Blue Devil head coaches.</p>
<p>"One thing I wish I had was the chin strap I got from him when he was a collegiate player at Florida," Cutcliffe said. "My brother [Paige] played with Spurrier at Florida, so I had his chin strap. And wouldn’t you know that somewhere along the way, it got lost. Not very smart on my part."</p>
                                    </div>

